item.title: [+585] President Obama's Historic First Female Helicopter Pilot
item.description: Maj. Jennifer Grieves is the first female helicopter aircraft commander in Marine One history. She has flown the president for the past 14 months. To mark her accomplishments, the Marines arranged for an all-female crew to accompany her on her last flight. President Obama also acknowledged her service when he came into the cockpit to thank her.
